# Planning Documents Location

Planning documents live in `.cursor/plans/`. They are working artifacts for the development process and should stay separate from the product code.

- Planning docs go in `.cursor/plans/` with naming convention `NNN_description.md`
- They contain implementation phases, acceptance criteria, and design decisions
- They reference the master plan (`000_observer_mvp_initial_plan.md`)
